OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,FHeadteachers in Blaenau Gwent have
OL,7,Fwarned parents that their children's
OL,8,Feducation will suffer because of the
OL,9,F"universally poor financial position"
OL,10,Fschools in the area find themselves in.
OL,12,FIn a letter, seen by ITV Wales, school
OL,13,Fleaders say they are at an
OL,14,F"unprecedented point" where there is
OL,15,F"nothing left to cut".
OL,17,FThey warn that additional learning
OL,18,Fneeds services and school trips could
OL,19,Fbe in danger amid growing budgetary
OL,20,Fpressures.
