OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,FBlaenau Gwent's Council leader says
OL,7,Fthey "fully acknowledge the
OL,8,Fsignificant financial pressures
OL,9,Fschools are facing due to high energy
OL,10,Fcosts, inflation and pay increases"
OL,11,Fwhile the Welsh Government say their
OL,12,Fbudget is worth #700m less in real
OL,13,Fterms than when it was set by the UK
OL,14,FGovernment in 2021.
OL,16,FITV Wales has contacted the Treasury
OL,17,Ffor a response.
