OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,FGlanhowy Primary School in Tredegar
OL,7,Fwas one of the schools where parents
OL,8,Freceived the letter setting out the
OL,9,Fdifficult financial situation
OL,10,Feducation in the area faces.
OL,12,F"It's not fair on the children," one
OL,13,Fparent told us while dropping their
OL,14,Fchild off at the gates.
OL,16,F"They're going to miss out. They
OL,17,Fshould be following the curriculum.
OL,18,FEverything should be about them and
OL,19,Ftheir learning style. It's just not
OL,20,Fgoing to happen with budget cuts."
