OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,FMaxine Edwards, who has three
OL,7,Fgrandchildren at the school, told us:
OL,8,F"(we were) very concerned (when we got
OL,9,Fthe letter). Obviously times are hard
OL,10,Fat the moment but we don't want these
OL,11,Fchildren's education to be affected.
OL,13,F"It's a dire situation at the moment.
OL,14,FThey've gone through enough trauma
OL,15,Fwith Covid and everything, as has
OL,16,Feverybody, but this generation, we've
OL,17,Fjust got to look after them and give
OL,18,Fthem the best experience through
OL,19,Fschool.
