OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,F"The cuts we are making now are just
OL,7,Fthe tip of the iceberg unfortunately.
OL,8,FWe know next year is going to be
OL,9,Freally difficult to have that vision
OL,10,Fand plan ahead in advance when we
OL,11,Fdon't know what our financial status
OL,12,Fis going to be.
OL,14,F"Lots of schools are going into
OL,15,Fdeficit budgets due to health and
OL,16,Fsafety issues in their schools. I
OL,17,Fthink that's just going to get worse
OL,18,Funless our funding improves and we are
OL,19,Ffunded fairly for our children in
OL,20,FWales."
