OL,6,FLeader of Blaenau Gwent council said
OL,7,Fin a statement that the "the future
OL,8,Ffor local authorities is grim" and the
OL,9,Fnext UK Government must make funding
OL,10,Fpublic services a priority.
OL,12,FCllr Steve Thomas said: "We fully
OL,13,Facknowledge the significant financial
OL,14,Fpressures schools are facing due to
OL,15,Fhigh energy costs, inflation and pay
OL,16,Fincreases.
