OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,F"Whilst cuts to budgets have been made
OL,7,Fright across the Local Authority, we
OL,8,Fdid not cut school budgets this year
OL,9,Fand have provided an additional
OL,10,F#864,000 to fund specific pressures,
OL,11,Fwhich is a 1.7% increase in real terms.
OL,13,F"As with all councils, we're gearing
OL,14,Fup for more tough financial
OL,15,Fchallenges. We must figure out how to
OL,16,Fsave around #26.5million million from
OL,17,Four budget over the next four years
OL,18,Fafter already enduring previous cuts
OL,19,Ftotalling #40 million.
