OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,F"Education remains a top priority for
OL,7,Fus, and we are extremely proud of the
OL,8,Fimprovement journey our schools and
OL,9,Feducation services have been on over
OL,10,Fthe past few years."
OL,12,FBlaenau Gwent Council is not in a
OL,13,Funique position. Every council in
OL,14,FWales is facing the prospect of
OL,15,Fmillions of pounds worth of saving
OL,16,Fhaving to be made or face huge
OL,17,Fblackholes in their budgets.
