OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,FThe National Association of
OL,7,FHeadteacher (NAHT) say the concerns
OL,8,Fare not a shock, having warned at the
OL,9,Fbeginning of this year that schools
OL,10,Ffaced a dire financial future.
OL,12,FLaura Doel, from NAHT Cymru, told us:
OL,13,F"Education is in crisis.
OL,15,F"Last year we took industrial action,
OL,16,Four members felt so strongly about the
OL,17,Ffunding in our schools and we are in
OL,18,Fconversations with our members about
OL,19,Fwhat to do next.
