OL,3,CSchool budgets: Headteachers warn
OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,F"We have to be clear: schools are
OL,7,Fstruggling to deliver statutory
OL,8,Feducation. If this continues we will
OL,9,Fbe forced to think again."
OL,11,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"Our budget for 2024-25 is now worth
OL,13,F#700m less in real terms than when it
OL,14,Fwas set by the UK Government in 2021.
OL,16,F"Despite this, we have prioritised
OL,17,Fcore frontline public services,
OL,18,Fincluding schools, through protecting
OL,19,Fthe indicative rise for the local
OL,20,Fgovernment settlement.
