OL,4,Cthere is 'nothing left to cut'
OL,6,F"The 2024-25 final settlement will
OL,7,Fprovide an additional 3.3% to local
OL,8,Fauthorities, on top of the
OL,9,Fconsolidated increase of 7.9% for 2023-
OL,10,F24.
OL,12,F"The amount of funding set aside for
OL,13,Fschool budgets is for local
OL,14,Fauthorities to determine and we will
OL,15,Fcontinue to work with the sector to
OL,16,Fensure the best possible outcomes for
OL,17,Four learners."
