OL,6,FIn response, Plaid Cymru said "It's
OL,7,Fclear both the Conservatives'
OL,8,Fprogramme of austerity and Labour's
OL,9,Fmismanagement of Welsh public spending
OL,10,Fhas resulted in public services in
OL,11,Fcrisis ` no more so than Wales'
OL,12,Feducation sector...
OL,14,F"Our children and young people deserve
OL,15,Fan education that provides them with
OL,16,Fthe tools they need for their future,
OL,17,Fand the workforce needs a government
OL,18,Fthat will act with urgency. Labour
OL,19,Fmust adequately fund schools if they
OL,20,Fare serious about prioritising future
OL,21,Fgenerations."
