OL,6,FMeanwhile the Conservatives said "It
OL,7,Fis unacceptable that headteachers are
OL,8,Fhaving to take such drastic action due
OL,9,Fto Labour's mismanagement of the
OL,10,Feducation budget, for every #1.20 that
OL,11,FLabour receive for education, they are
OL,12,Fonly spending #1.05.
OL,14,F"The Labour Government have overseen a
OL,15,Fdecline in standards over their 25
OL,16,Fyears in charge and by cutting the
OL,17,Feducation budget in real terms and
OL,18,Fcash terms they are leaving schools
OL,19,Fand local authorities struggling to
OL,20,Fmake ends meet. "
